rican Heart Association National Heart, Lung, and Blood Institute Children High Cholesterol in Children and Teens: MedlinePlus Health Topic (National Library of Medicine) Also in Spanish Patient Handouts Cholesterol and lifestyle (Medical Encyclopedia) Also in Spanish Cholesterol testing and results (Medical Encyclopedia) Also in Spanish Familial combined hyperlipidemia (Medical Encyclopedia) Also in Spanish Familial hypercholesterolemia (Medical Encyclopedia) Also in Spanish High cholesterol - children (Medical Encyclopedia) Also in Spanish', 'NIH_MedlinePlus', 'cholesterol', 'https://medlineplus.gov/cholesterol.html', 'patient_education', '{"content_hash": "0cd231606c912501", "embedding_date": "2025-06-25T14:20:42.637396", "scraper_source": "NIH_MedlinePlus", "category": "patient_education", "subcategory": "medlineplus", "document_type": "patient_education", "published_date": "", "original_url": "https://medlineplus.gov/cholesterol.html"}', 10496);

